WEBVTT

00:00.055 --> 00:01.832
This is what I've been telling you about,...

00:02.276 --> 00:04.498
...that I've dreamed of since I was your age.

00:07.101 --> 00:11.306
Yeah, like the boy in the movie that floats with the balloon.

00:11.510 --> 00:15.157
And what I want to do is I want to grab that rig of balloons...

00:15.532 --> 00:19.057
...and I want to go floating all the way up into the sky...

00:19.313 --> 00:22.644
...until I become a little dot in the sky that you're gonna see.

00:23.027 --> 00:23.517
I will see?

00:23.747 --> 00:26.211
Yeah, you're gonna be able to watch me go all the way up.

00:26.318 --> 00:27.340
A little black dot.

00:27.449 --> 00:29.204
And where am I gonna head towards?

00:29.533 --> 00:30.141
Venus.

00:30.241 --> 00:33.187
Yeah, but not that far, of course.

00:33.845 --> 00:34.492
I hope so.

00:35.717 --> 00:37.263
And this was all because of you.

